PROGRAM TO PRINT A STAIR PATTERN USING LOOPS IN C:

I/P:

#include <stdio.h>
void main()
{
   int i,j,rows;
   printf("Input number of stairs : ");
   scanf("%d",&rows);
   for(i=0;i<=rows;i++)
   {
	for(j=1;j<=i;j++)
	   printf("01 ");
	   printf("\ ");
   }
}

O/P:

Input number of stairs : 6
01  01 01  01 01 01  01 01 01 01  01 01 01 01 01  01 01 01 01 01 01 
